fields.name: Samsung Galaxy S23 Ultra
fields.description: The Samsung Galaxy S23 Ultra offers a 200MP camera, a massive 6.8-inch Dynamic AMOLED display, and a powerful Snapdragon 8 Gen 2 processor. Its robust design and excellent camera capabilities make it a top-tier flagship.

fields.name: Apple iPhone 15 Pro Max
fields.description: The iPhone 15 Pro Max features a cutting-edge A17 Pro chip, a 48MP camera system, and a 6.7-inch OLED display. The phone supports 5G connectivity and boasts impressive battery life with a sleek design.

fields.name: Dell XPS 13 (2023)
fields.description: The Dell XPS 13 (2023) is a high-performance ultrabook featuring a 13.4-inch InfinityEdge display, 12th-generation Intel Core processors, and a sleek design with premium materials. It's perfect for professionals and content creators.
